#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.multilabel_confusion_matrix.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.multilabel\\_confusion\\_matrix"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:1 of
msgid "Compute a confusion matrix for each class or sample."
msgstr "为每个类别或样本计算混淆矩阵。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:3 of
msgid ""
"Compute class-wise (default) or sample-wise (samplewise=True) multilabel "
"confusion matrix to evaluate the accuracy of a classification, and output"
" confusion matrices for each class or sample."
msgstr ""
"按类别（默认）或按样本（samplewise=True）计算多标签混淆矩阵，以评估分类的"
"准确性，并输出每个类别或样本的混淆矩阵。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:7 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"In multilabel confusion matrix :math:`MCM`, the count of true negatives "
"is :math:`MCM_{:,0,0}`, false negatives is :math:`MCM_{:,1,0}`, true "
"positives is :math:`MCM_{:,1,1}` and false positives is "
":math:`MCM_{:,0,1}`."
msgstr ""
"在多标签混淆矩阵 :math:`MCM` 中，真负例数为 :math:`MCM_{:,0,0}`，假负例数"
"为 :math:`MCM_{:,1,0}`，真正例数为 :math:`MCM_{:,1,1}`，假正例数为 :math:"
"`MCM_{:,0,1}`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:12 of
msgid ""
"Multiclass data will be treated as if binarized under a one-vs-rest "
"transformation. Returned confusion matrices will be in the order of "
"sorted unique labels in the union of (y_true, y_pred)."
msgstr ""
"多类数据将被视为通过一对一转换进行二值化处理。返回的混淆矩阵将按照 (y_"
"true, y_pred) 并集中排序后的唯一标签顺序排列。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:16 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <multilabel_confusion_matrix>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <multilabel_confusion_matrix>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:18 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:20 of
msgid "Estimated targets as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "由分类器返回的预测目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:22 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:24 of
msgid ""
"A list of classes or column indices to select some (or to force inclusion"
" of classes absent from the data)."
msgstr "一个类别或列索引列表，用于选择某些类别（或强制包含数据中缺失的类别）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:27 of
msgid "In the multilabel case, this calculates a confusion matrix per sample."
msgstr "在多标签情况下，这将为每个样本计算一个混淆矩阵。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:30 of
msgid ""
"**multi_confusion** -- A 2x2 confusion matrix corresponding to each "
"output in the input. When calculating class-wise multi_confusion "
"(default), then n_outputs = n_labels; when calculating sample-wise "
"multi_confusion (samplewise=True), n_outputs = n_samples. If ``labels`` "
"is defined, the results will be returned in the order specified in "
"``labels``, otherwise the results will be returned in sorted order by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"**multi_confusion** -- 与输入中每个输出对应的 2x2 混淆矩阵。当按类别计算 "
"multi_confusion（默认）时，n_outputs = n_labels；当按样本计算 multi_"
"confusion（samplewise=True）时，n_outputs = n_samples。如果定义了 ``"
"labels``，结果将按 ``labels`` 中指定的顺序返回，否则默认按排序顺序返回。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`confusion_matrix`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:41 of
msgid "Compute confusion matrix to evaluate the accuracy of a classifier."
msgstr "计算混淆矩阵以评估分类器的准确性。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:44 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.multilabel_confusion_matrix:45 of
msgid ""
"The `multilabel_confusion_matrix` calculates class-wise or sample-wise "
"multilabel confusion matrices, and in multiclass tasks, labels are "
"binarized under a one-vs-rest way; while "
":func:`~sklearn.metrics.confusion_matrix` calculates one confusion matrix"
" for confusion between every two classes."
msgstr ""
"`multilabel_confusion_matrix` 按类别或按样本计算多标签混淆矩阵，在多类"
"任务中，标签采用一对一方式进行二值化；而 :func:`~sklearn.metrics."
"confusion_matrix` 则计算每两个类别之间的单一混淆矩阵。"

